body:
So yeah we all know we have a lot of YouTube channels and only a handful of them have even 100 subs. How are we going to advertise Avicus if everyone who makes Avicus videos have like 40 subs on average? More people will subscribe to someone if they have 100 subs than if they have 60, so IMO we should subscribe to as many Avicus youtubers (or at least check their channels out) so they get a bit more "out there" and can promote Avicus better. So type out your channels down below! :D
www.youtube.com/MiguelPlayz
and please don't take this as spam. :P
Also, we Avicus youtubers should do collaborations, shouldn't we? 
So add your Skype too :P
Skype : miguelplaysmc
